# Intern 5: Async/Await

- Prefer `async`/`await` over nested `.then()` chains in UI event handlers.
- Set loading state before awaiting work.
- Reset loading state in a `finally` block so failures cannot leave the button stuck.
- Keep success, error, and cleanup paths easy to read.
- Run the app and verify the button text changes while data loads.
